The Gift of Love, Multiplied through Our Beautiful Couple, Family & Friends
We are Incredibly Blessed
🙏🏼Thank God🙏🏼
🤍🤍🤍🤍🤍🤍
🤍Many Thanks to Joe Zisa @djexpressnj for surprising us with this clip to relive the Magical Evening over & over
🤍Aleka @alexecoevents for planning & creating this enchantingly ethereal Day & Evening @pleasantdalechateau
